Home|Spa Products|SHOCK & OXIDIZE



SHOCK & OXIDIZE
Step 3 of the hth Spa™ Care 3-Step System is to shock or oxidize your spa water. Shocking your spa water weekly will help keep your water clean and clear by removing organic contaminants that can build up in the water.






1
Balance




2
Sanitize




3
Shock & Oxidize




4
Algaecide




5
Specialty


Step 3: Shock & Oxidize


SPA SHOCKS & OXIDIZERS



hth spa™ Non-Chlorinating Shock Oxidizer

Clears cloudy water
Eliminates odors and contaminants

Don't know which products you need? Visit our water testing section.

