These brands are sold in the company's own shops, as well as to independent distributors such as department stores, duty-free shops, and opticians.
Retail[edit]
Luxottica Retail has approximately 8,000 retail locations[1] in the United States, Latin America, Canada, China, Australia, New Zealand, South Africa, the United Kingdom, and United Arab Emirates.[15] The headquarters of the retail division is in Mason, Ohio, United States (North America).[15] Their retail banners include the following:[29]


Sunglass Hut International
Apex by Sunglass Hut
LensCrafters
Pearle Vision
Sears Optical
Target Optical
OPSM
ILORI
